.TH LIGHTNING-CHANNEL-UPTIME-SKEWNESS 1
.SH NAME
lightning-channel-uptime-skewness \- compute skewness of channel uptime distribution
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning channel-uptime-skewness
.SH DESCRIPTION
Queries listpeerchannels and computes the skewness of the uptime distribution across channels.
.SH OUTPUT
JSON object with field \fBuptime_skewness\fR.
